{"tid":182221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[搞大佢] 垃圾page偷片仲要落ad，三十萬人like","createTime":"2017-04-01T07:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T17:23:18.000Z","uid":42164,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ba11ca0e84a3eac913d47283f51b852ce05f7f8","tid":182221,"uid":42164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近King jer咪剪咗條Chef le M&oacute;n(港譯：謝檸檬)煮飯既片<br />\n有朋友偶然發現有個垃圾page<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【ALIVE Hong Kong】</span>成條片再upload，完全冇落credit俾King jer<br />\n原來嗰個page條條片都係偷返嚟，而且仲要落ad推page<br />\n但係個page竟然有 <span style=\"color: red;\">超過三十萬個like</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂大佬，二次創作都係創作，俾返少少尊重其他創作人得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朋友已經喺佢個post到留言，但冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個page仲有繼續出新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPM咗King jer，但暫時未見King jer有其他行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢啲垃圾偷片page仲有好多，但咁公然偷片仲落埋廣告真係好撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鄭重呼籲所有連登巴打們一齊搞大佢，一定要推到個page摺埋為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b0tq893n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb0tq893n&h=dc9953d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ebgsi8wr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Febgsi8wr&h=66694ee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7709cf7b4c34d752c7b29d8403df65621f8e6259","tid":182221,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a87ca32335d3bd8eb4d0eea97fff8651cc1e45b5","tid":182221,"uid":11506,"l